text:
@JoyFaheyArtist  I really admire your work and method. I've been exploring intuitive painting myself recently and have found your videos, and your perspectives so valuable. 

Thank you for sharing your vulnerability with us. It is such a provoking piece. Better out than in indeed. I am excited for all the love and light that will no doubt be flowing into your life as this flows out onto the canvas.

My heart goes out to you.
